high_descs: Turn right and move towards the door next to the refrigerator then turn right and move to the table next to the chair.
Pick up the spoon on the left corner of the table in front of the apple.
Turn around and move towards the toaster next to the refrigerator then turn left and move to the sink in front of the window.
Place the spoon in the wine glass next to the spatula in the sink.
Pick up the wine glass containing the spoon from the sink
Turn around and move towards the refrigerator next to the door then turn right and move to the table with the wine bottle on top.
Place the wine glass containing the spoon on the table in the position left of the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Place a wine glass containing a spoon on the table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk so you are even with the white table on your right then turn right and walk to the table so you are facing the left side of it looking at the wall.
Pick up the spoon near the edge that's sitting under an apple.
Turn around and walk to the sink so you are facing the right side of the sink.
Put the spoon in the wine glass.
Pick up the wine glass with a spoon in it.
Walk back to the table where you got the spoon.
Put the glass with the spoon in it near the edge of the table to the right of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a wine glass with a spoon in it on the white table.

high_descs: Turn around, go to the long side of the white table.
Take the spoon near the apple on the table.
Turn right, go to the right sink.
Put the spoon in the glass in the sink.
Take the glass from the sink.
Turn around, go to the long side of the white table on the right.
Put the glass near the lower left corner of the sponge on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with a spoon in it on a table.
